{
  "texts": [
    "The practical utilization and real-world impact of blockchain in the sports sector remain relatively unexplored.",
    "While there have been two reviews examining the integration of blockchain technology in sports, we argue that these reviews do not comprehensively address the subject and its potential applications.",
    "In the research conducted by Schillinger et al. [18], the authors successfully identified and categorized blockchain use cases in sports.",
    "However, the technical implementation details and practical aspects of employing blockchain in this domain receive limited coverage.",
    "Conversely, in the study by Lopez et al. [19], blockchain's role in sports is extensively discussed, albeit solely within the context of one application area (athlete data management)."
  ]
}